  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/18a9c4a62ba051f17e1c028760fd3860.avif?t=1767149454\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras_big/18a9c4a62ba051f17e1c028760fd3860.avif?t=1767149454 width=1424 height=8192 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/1c47156bc016a88638fe354c4665991d.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/1c47156bc016a88638fe354c4665991d.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/1c47156bc016a88638fe354c4665991d.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rune Coliseum is an action-packed gladiator battle simulator that combines elements from deck-building, fighting, and roguelike games. Pick a character, prepare for a duel, and enter the deadly tournament where only one can emerge as the victor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/3207610d71dd82e2b45f50208c8e143f.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/3207610d71dd82e2b45f50208c8e143f.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/3207610d71dd82e2b45f50208c8e143f.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the unique combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique turn-based combat system where you can perform multiple actions in a single turn; it combines strategic depth with smooth animations. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Fighter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/8e76a0d1d4a2510989997adb10a732dc.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=156 /></span>Pick one gladiator from many to start the battle, each with unique skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/614fc71831422719233633255caf7cec.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/614fc71831422719233633255caf7cec.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/614fc71831422719233633255caf7cec.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/416ba87320ebc3b4bcab24287e40e55c.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=156 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experiment with Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunder a wide variety of weapons and equipment from other players on the battlefield, or purchase them at shops. Each item has its own unique skills, allowing you to customize your playstyle and tactics to suit your preferences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/a4d68d9893f0e034cc4eddb2e7b92569.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=178 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine Runes to Gain More Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine moves and magic runes inside the special build, devastating skills that can turn the tide of the battle in your favor.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/1c47156bc016a88638fe354c4665991d.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/1c47156bc016a88638fe354c4665991d.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/1c47156bc016a88638fe354c4665991d.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rune Coliseum is an action-packed gladiator battle simulator that combines elements from deck-building, fighting, and roguelike games. Pick a character, prepare for a duel, and enter the deadly tournament where only one can emerge as the victor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/3207610d71dd82e2b45f50208c8e143f.poster.avif?t=1767149454\" width=616 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/3207610d71dd82e2b45f50208c8e143f.webm?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360210/extras/3207610d71dd82e2b45f50208c8e143f.mp4?t=1767149454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master the unique combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique turn-based combat system where you can perform multiple actions in a single turn; it combines strategic depth with smooth animations. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Fighter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><s